HEADWORD: Dieffenbachia
<hw>Dieffenbachia</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>a genus of evergreen perennial
herbs of tropical America with lush foliage and poisonous sap; often
cultivated as houseplants.</def>⟦br⟧
